@startuml rain_light_and_wiper_cmd_to_wiper_anim_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Rain Light And Wiper Cmd To Wiper Anim Signal Flow\n(rain/light input + manual wiper command -> WIP state and animation frame)

participant "Rain / light sensor bus" as Rain #F4F7FB
participant "Manual control\nCmd::wiperCmd" as Manual #E8F0FE
participant "WIP\nwiper owner" as WIP #E8F7E8
participant "Body seams /\nwiper state bus" as BodyBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\npanel renderers" as Obs #FCE8FF

== Wiper Inputs ==

Rain -> WIP : frmRainLightAutoMsg\nRainSenseLevel / AutoLightState
Manual -> WIP : Cmd::wiperCmd\n(when scenarioActiveId == 0)
activate WIP
WIP -> WIP : rainInputStale =\nethIsRecentTick(gRainRxMs, 300)
WIP -> WIP : if stale then\nrainSenseLevel = 0 / autoLightState = 0
WIP -> WIP : derive FrontWiperState /\nRearWiperState / WiperInterval
WIP -> WIP : advance gWiperPos using\nstate-derived step and direction
note right of WIP
Representative gating inputs
- RainSenseLevel
- AutoLightState
- Cmd::wiperCmd
- scenarioActiveId gate
end note

== Wiper Publish ==

WIP -> BodyBus : frmWiperStateMsg\nFrontWiperState / RearWiperState / WiperInterval
WIP -> BodyBus : Body::wiperPos\nBody::frontWiperAnimFrame
note right of WIP
Representative outputs
- FrontWiperState
- RearWiperState
- WiperInterval
- frontWiperAnimFrame
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

BodyBus -> Obs : body readback /\nwiper animation and panel observers
deactivate WIP

note over Rain, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Rain/light state and manual wiper command reach WIP
2. WIP chooses manual or sensed wiper posture
3. WIP derives interval and animation position
4. WIP publishes frmWiperStateMsg and Body animation seams
end note

@enduml
